    "bbox": [
      58.56,
      460.99,
      538.36,
      516.79
    ],
    "text": "Issued at 04.00 p.m. on 15 April 2026. Showers or thundershowers will occur at several places in Western, Sabaragamuwa, Southern, Uva and North-western provinces, and in Kandy and Nuwara-Eliya districts after 1.00 pm.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri,Bold"
    ],
